======================================================================

To build Serpents from a git checkout, you will need autotools in
addition to SDL2 and SDL_ttf. First run:

    $ autoreconf -vif

Then:

    $ ./configure
    $ make

For serpents to be able to find the required data files, you should
also install it using `make install' once. After doing that you can
run the executable generated with `make' on its own,
e.g. `./src/serpents'.
